# 04 — Review Process

**Every change requires review.**

## Review checklist

| Area | Verify |
|------|--------|
| Requirements | Diff matches stated task scope only |
| Architecture | No ADR-level change without approval |
| Tests | Executed tests reported honestly; unrun = NOT VERIFIED |
| Documentation | SRS, ADR/EDL, affected docs updated |
| Risks | Assumptions, regressions, open questions listed |

## Document statuses (authorized use only)

Concept · Proposed · Under Review · Approved for DevKit · Approved for Prototype · Verified · Deprecated

Do not mark Approved or Verified without explicit instruction.

## Traceability

Preserve requirement IDs. Reference ADR/EDL for decisions. Do not renumber requirements without authorization.

Templates: `docs/templates/Architecture_Review_Template.md`, `docs/templates/Work_Package_Template.md`.

See `docs/REVIEW_PROCESS.md`.
